North Sudan Attacks South Sudan Border Village; 1 Death, South Sudan Says

-- B y   M a t t   R i c h m o n d
-- 
2011-06-09T15:31:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/north-sudan-attacks-south-sudan-border-village-1-death-south-sudan-says.html
One civilian was killed when two
northern Sudanese antonov planes bombed a Southern Sudanese
village in oil-rich Unity state on the border with northern
 Sudan , Gideon Gatpan, Unity state information minister, said
today by phone from Bentiu, the state capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
